comments: Ayton (POR) briefly places his hand to Haliburton's (IND) body, which Haliburton is able to move through.
Turner (IND) delivers contact to Walker's (POR) head as he attempts to pursue the rebound.
Nesmith (IND) moves alongside Brogdon's (POR) path and the body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt when both players come together is marginal.
Ayton (POR) makes contact with the ball while it is still in the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Thybulle (POR) grabs and holds onto Haliburton's (IND) arm as the inbounds pass is released, which affects his FOM.
Nesmith (IND) grazes Brogdon's (POR) arm after he receives the inbounds pass, which does not affect his control of the ball.
Nesmith (IND) brushes Brogdon's (POR) lower body during the drive, which Brogdon is able to move through.
Haliburton (IND) reaches in and makes clean contact to the ball after Brogdon's (POR) gather on his driving shot attempt.
Haliburton (IND) steps into the backcourt while in possession of the ball.
Siakam (IND) reaches in and makes slight contact to Thybulle's (IND) arm, which does not affect his control of the ball.
Ayton (POR) establishes himself in Siakam's (IND) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Hield (IND) makes contact with the ball, causing it to become loose during Grant's (POR) driving shot attempt and any further contact is incidental.
The shot clock expires when the ball is loose and before Indiana gains possession of the ball.
Hield (IND) maintains an arm against Grant's (POR) side and initiates illegal contact when he reaches across Grant's body.
Haliburton (IND) releases the inbounds pass within five seconds.
Nesmith (IND) commits a take foul on Walker (POR).
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that both Walker (POR) and Nesmith (IND) would be assessed technical fouls.  All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.

Thybulle (POR) cleanly blocks Haliburton's (IND) jump shot attempt.
